  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chilis and onions; sauté until softened about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in garlic and peppers, cook for another minute.",
    "Mix in tomato paste, cumin, paprika, salt, black pepper, and lime juice. Stir well.",
    "Gently fold in tempeh and simmer for 5-7 minutes until heated through and tempeh is chewy.",
    "Serve immediately."
